<hw>Stat"u*a</hw> <pr>(st⟦acr⟧t"⟦usl⟧*⟦adot⟧)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[L.]</ety> <def>A statue.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
